  "title": "(ASAP!) Sales Associate (No experience needed!)",
  "description": "<p><em><strong>Sales Associate | No Experience? Training provided! | Fresh grad welcome!</strong></em><br /></p><p>We are looking for a motivates <strong>Sales Associate </strong>to support our business growth by engaging with clients, understanding their needs, and building long-term relationships. This role offer hands-on exposure, real results, and strong career development in as supportive team environment.<br /></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong><br /><strong>- </strong>Engage and communicate with clients to understand their business needs. <br />- Promote suitanle solutions in a proffesional and consultative manner <br />-Support sales and business development initiatives <br />-Participate in corporate outreach, events or roadshows<br />Maintain accurate records and follow up with clients professionally <br /></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong><br /><strong>- </strong>Comfortable communicating with people<br />- Motivated, responsible, and willing to learn <br />- Comfortable working in a fast-paced environment</p><p><strong>Benifits:</strong><br /><strong>- </strong>Performance bases incentives<br />- 1-1 training provided <br />- Clear career progression<br />- Supportive, dynamic, and collaborative work environment <br /></p><p><em><strong>Apply now - the crew’s waiting for you!</strong></em></p>",
